<h1>Password Reset</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>

<p>Click on the link below to continue with the password reset process:</p>

<%= link_to "Reset Password", edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token,
    email: @user.email) %>

<p>This link will expire in two hours.</p>

<p>If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email
and your password will stay as it is.
</p>
